    "body": " I think the fact that the first line isn't hidden in the hover window is because the cursor is on that that line. Presumably it would be concealed if the LSP hover window added `vim.o.concealcursor = 'n'`. Though I think it _should_ be concealed if the hover is not yet the current window, that seems to be a bug.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @luukvbaal in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/31324#issuecomment-2672707939_\r\n            ",
